She was born on December 20, 1987, in Kolkata, West Bengal, India.

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

Mishti gained recognition for her debut role as the female lead in the Bollywood film "Kaanchi: The Unbreakable"

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

After her debut, Mishti Chakraborty appeared in several Hindi, Telugu, and Bengali films
